  "about": "Birthdate: March 21\nHeight: 165 cm\nWeight: 50 kg\nBlood type: O\nHobby: Net Surfing\nLikes: Living a different life, Sonohara Anri\nDislikes: Living a normal life\nHandle: Tanaka Tarou (田中太郎)\n\nThe primary male protagonist of the series, Mikado Ryugamine is a high school boy who moved to Ikebukuro with the encouragement of his best friend Masaomi in order to search for unusual beings and adventure. Mikado tries hard to change his image but so far he has not had any luck. Mikado has had moments where he speaks his mind, which is a reason why Masaomi admires him.",
